snippet.title: Stronghold HD - Steam Trailer (2016)
snippet.description:
Out Now on Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/40950/

The original 'Castle Sim', Stronghold HD allows you to design, build and destroy historical castles. Engage in medieval warfare against the AI in one of two single player campaigns or online with up to 8 players. With 21 missions to test your mettle and four renegade lords to defeat, it is up to you to reunite medieval England and take back your lands from the treacherous Rat, Pig, Snake and Wolf.

Like - http://bit.ly/FFfbook

Subscribe - http://bit.ly/fftubesub
Play - http://bit.ly/stronghd
